data.eml:eml: Checklist of acanthocephalan parasites of South Africa

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Halajian, Ali, Smales, Lesley R., Tavakol, Sareh, Smit, Nico J., Wilmien J. Luus-Powell, (2018): Checklist of acanthocephalan parasites of South Africa. ZooKeys 789: 1-18, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.789.27710, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.789.27710
